cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically parser adaptation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses neural networks for the parser. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with adapting a model to new domains. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as parsing is often used in information retrieval tasks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for the parser adaptation.
